RitesPortal
===========

This is a Rails Engine plugin designed to implement portal functionality such that would be used in schools. It will have:

- Districts
- Schools
- Teachers
- Students
- Classes
- etc.

Installation
============
run: script/plugin install git://github.com/psndcsrv/rites_portal.git
add: 'map.from_plugin :rites_portal' to your config/routes.rb
run: script/generate plugin_migration
run: rake db:migrate


